# Backend origin for the split deploy. The frontend (this app) is a static Vite
# build; the Express API runs separately (Render). Leave empty for local dev when
# the backend serves same-origin, or when using the Vite dev proxy (vite.config.ts).
#
# In production (Vercel), set this in the project's Environment Variables.
VITE_API_BASE=https://stredio.onrender.com
